The [statements](https://github.com/visionmedia/debug/blob/3.2.6/src/browser.js#L72) in [debug](https://www.npmjs.com/package/debug) library are:
```
  args[0].replace(/%[a-zA-Z%]/g, function (match) {
    if (match === '%%') {
      return;
    }

    index++;

    if (match === '%c') {
      // We only are interested in the *last* %c
      // (the user may have provided their own)
      lastC = index;
    }
  });
```

but after `ng build --prod`, it turns:
```
e[0].replace(/%[a-zA-Z%]/g, function (t) {
        '%%' !== t && '%c' === t && (i = ++r);
    })
```
where ++r (index++) is misplaced after uglified.

